text: James and Harry are trying on different shirts to see if James can pull off the same rock star looks that Harry can. While in a shiny gold top, Harry observes, “It’s a bit nipplly.” Cut to a wide shot and we see James in a fishnet top, saying, “Yours is nipply? My actual nipple is through.”Watch Harry Styles on The Late Late Show all this week at 12:37am/11:37pm c on CBS and stream full episodes on CBS All Access
